Compiled by 3M (in promotion of their reflective material):


Pedestrians account for one out of every six traffic fatalities.* 

Thirty-five percent of all bicycle fatalities occur at night, even
though only seven percent of cycling miles occur then.**

Sixty-six percent of all pedestrian accidents occur at twilight, dusk
or night.***

 *AAA Foundation for Traffic Safety
 **U.S. Consumer Product Safety Commission
 ***National Safety Council
